metadata.name: Metaplaces Offices 1
metadata.description: Metaplaces Offices will redefine how people meet and collaborate in the Metaverse. Holders get a free website for life on Sitecreator.io worth several hundred dollars and can use their office for videoconferences. Own a rare breathtaking office designed by talented architects. Invite clients and coworkers to your spacious office in 3D by sharing your own URL. Organize productive meetings in the conference room. Customize your offices logo, furniture and portraits as you see fit. Don't miss anything thanks to the Slack integration. Turn your office into an organic lead acquisition tool with CRM and Calendar integrations.
